    <title type="text">BIBLindex: Références bibliques dans la littérature patristique</title>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-size:
      xx-small;">[First posted in AWOL 9 December 2009. Updated 30 March 2015]</span>
      </span><br /><br /><a
      href="https://www.blogger.com/blogger.g?blogID=116259103207720939" imageanchor="1"
      style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"></a><a
      href="http://www.biblindex.mom.fr/"><span style="font-size: small;">BIBLindex<span
      style="color: black;"><span style="color: black;">:</span>
      </span>Références bibliques dans la littérature patristique</span></a><br
      /><blockquote class="tr_bq"></blockquote><blockquote class="tr_bq"><img
      alt="http://www.biblindex.mom.fr/templates/rhuk_milkyway/images/mw_joomla_logo.png"
      class="transparent"
      src="http://www.biblindex.mom.fr/templates/rhuk_milkyway/images/mw_joomla_logo.png"
      /></blockquote><blockquote><span style="font-size: x-small;"><b>A
      corpus of about 400,000 biblical references is available on this
      site.</b></span><br /><div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span
      style="font-size: x-small;"><br /></span></div><span style="font-size:
      x-small;"><b><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Access to
      data is free. This website offers:</span></b></span>
      </blockquote><blockquote><span style="font-size: x-small;"><b><span
      style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; line-height: 115%;">- Data from the
      published volumes of </span><span style="font-family:
      arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><i><span style="line-height: 115%;">Biblia
      Patristica,</span></i></span></b><span style="font-family:
      arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><i><span style="line-height: 115%;"> Index des
      citations et allusions bibliques dans la littérature patristique,
      </span></i></span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;
      line-height: 115%;">Editions du CNRS </span><span style="font-family:
      arial,helvetica,sans-serif; line-height: 115%;">(ca. </span><span
      style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; line-height: 115%;">270,000 biblical
      references, with updates on 5,000 references), prepared by </span><b><a
      href="http://theopro.unistra.fr/recherche/histoire-du-christianisme/cadp/" target="_blank"
      title="CADP">the Centre for Patristics Analysis and Documentation
      (CADP)</a></b><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; line-height:
      115%;"> : 1. <b>Beginnings to Clement of Alexandria and Tertullian</b>, 1975 -
      2. <b>The third century</b> (except Origen), 1977 - 3. <b>Origen</b>,
      1980 - 4. <b>Eusebius of Caesarea, Cyril of Jerusalem, Epiphanius of Salamis</b>,
      1987 - 5.<a href="http://www.cnrseditions.fr/ouvrage/5080.html" target="_blank">
      </a><b>Basil of Caesarea, Gregory Nazianzen, Gregory of Nyssa, Amphiloque of
      Iconium</b>, 1991 - 6. <b>Hilary of Poitiers, Ambrose of Milan,
      Ambrosiaster</b>, 1995 - 7. <b>Didymus of Alexandria</b>, 2000 - Supplement,
      <b>Philo of Alexandria</b>, 1982. [They all are all out of
      print.]</span></span> </blockquote><blockquote><span
      style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-family:
      arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><b>- Unpublished data </b>from the archives of
      <i>Biblia Patristica</i> (ca. 100,000 references) on <b>Athanasius of
      Alexandria, John Chrysostom, Theodoret of Cyrus, Procopius of Gaza, Jerome</b>: these
      data are unverified (they appear in
      red).</span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="tr_bq"><span
      style="font-size: x-small;"><b>For further information on our project, please visit
      our scientific blog: <a href="http://biblindex-en.hypotheses.org/?lang=en_GB"
      target="_blank" title="Biblindex on
      Hypotheses.org">http://biblindex.hypotheses.org/.</a></b>
      </span></blockquote><blockquote class="tr_bq"><span style="font-size:
      x-small;"></span><span style="font-size: x-small;">The project is supported by
      the French Research Agency (ANR, 2011-2015):<b> a new version of this site is currently
      prepared. Thank you for your understanding.</b></span></blockquote>]]></content>
